OL,3,CRochdale groomers 'destroyed my life',
OL,4,Cvictims tell court
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist Emma
OL,7,FSweeney was in court to hear the
OL,8,Fimpact statements from two girls
OL,10,FThe schoolgirl victims of an Asian
OL,11,Fgrooming gang have told a court their
OL,12,Flives have been "put on hold" for the
OL,13,Fpast 20 years after their abusers
OL,14,F"destroyed" their lives.
OL,16,FThe seven men treated the two girls,
OL,17,Fwho were just 13 when the abuse began,
OL,18,Fas "sex-slaves", befriending them and
OL,19,Fplying them with alcohol before raping
OL,20,Fand sexually abusing them in Rochdale
OL,21,Fbetween 2001 and 2006.
