OL,6,FBoth told Manchester Minshull Street
OL,7,FCrown Court the abuse had not only
OL,8,Faffect their lives, but that of their
OL,9,Ffamily's as well.
OL,11,FThe victim personal statement of the
OL,12,Fvictims, known as Girl A and Girl B,
OL,13,Fwere read out ahead of the sentencing
OL,14,Fof seven men who were convicted in
OL,15,FJune of various child sex offences.
