OL,3,CRochdale groomers 'destroyed my life',
OL,4,Cvictims tell court
OL,6,FThey were expected to have sex
OL,7,F"whenever and wherever" the defendants
OL,8,Fand other men wanted, in filthy flats,
OL,9,Fon rancid mattresses, in cars, car
OL,10,Fparks, alleyways and disused
OL,11,Fwarehouses, the court was told.
OL,13,FDuring the trial, Girl A told the jury
OL,14,Fshe could have been targeted by more
OL,15,Fthan 200 offenders as her phone number
OL,16,Fwas swapped but said "there was that
OL,17,Fmany it was hard to keep count".
