OL,3,CRochdale groomers 'destroyed my life',
OL,4,Cvictims tell court
OL,6,FIn a statement read out by prosecutor
OL,7,FRossano Scamardella KC, during the
OL,8,Fsentencing hearing, Girl A said: "My
OL,9,Flife has been destroyed from the abuse
OL,10,Fof these men.
OL,12,F"The abuse has affected every part of
OL,13,Fmy life, from what I look like,
OL,14,Frelationships, health, to my mental
OL,15,Fhealth.
OL,17,F"Over the last 10 years when I finally
OL,18,Fplucked up the courage to approach the
OL,19,Fpolice and disclose the abuse I
OL,20,Fsuffered, it has been an absolute
OL,21,Femotional rollercoaster for me.
OL,26,@pD@bOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
