OL,3,CRochdale groomers 'destroyed my life',
OL,4,Cvictims tell court
OL,6,F"I have provided about 40 video
OL,7,Finterviews having to speak about what
OL,8,FI was subjected to, talking about it
OL,9,Fout loud and explaining it in detail.
OL,11,F"This has been and still is consuming
OL,12,Fmy life. I hope that one day I will be
OL,13,Fable to move forward with my life.
OL,15,F"The jury finding these men guilty I
OL,16,Fhope is going to help me take another
OL,17,Fstep forward to get my life back, as I
OL,18,Fhave already lost my childhood.
