OL,3,CRochdale groomers 'destroyed my life',
OL,4,Cvictims tell court
OL,6,FShe said: "I coped with what these men
OL,7,Fdid to me as at the time I believed
OL,8,Fthat every man I came into contact
OL,9,Fwith would expect sex. It is horrific
OL,10,Fthat I didn't know any different.
OL,12,F"My way of coping was to block out
OL,13,Fmost of what had been done to me. I
OL,14,Fhave felt shame and guilt all my life
OL,15,Ffor what these men did.
OL,17,F"My life has been on hold for the last
OL,18,F20 years, I have never been able to
OL,19,Fmove on from the abuse.
