OL,6,F"This has not just impacted my life
OL,7,Fand what I could have achieved, but
OL,8,Falso my children's lives. They have
OL,9,Fbecome victims of these men too.
OL,11,F"Before the CSE (child sexual
OL,12,Fexploitation) team came to me I had no
OL,13,Ffaith in the police, but meeting
OL,14,Fsomeone who believed and understood
OL,15,Feverything meant I could trust for the
OL,16,Ffirst time.
OL,18,F"It is important that people know that
OL,19,Fthe team who have worked on my case
OL,20,Fhave been amazing.
