OL,3,CRochdale groomers 'destroyed my life',
OL,4,Cvictims tell court
OL,6,F"People in the press and social media
OL,7,Fhave told victims of CSE not to go to
OL,8,Fthe police. This is wrong.
OL,10,F"I want these victims to know that if
OL,11,Fthey feel ready to deal with what
OL,12,Fhappened to them they shouldn't wait,
OL,13,Fthey should go to the CSE team because
OL,14,Fthey will do a good job.
OL,16,F"It doesn't matter how much time has
OL,17,Fgone by, it is still possible to get
OL,18,Fjustice.
